  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Engaging diasporas for an alternative approach to safer shelters in disaster response and preparedness</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this pilot programme IOM aims to increase the awareness of selected US based diaspora groups on the importance of safer shelters for disaster response and preparedness as well as, identify and promote, in cooperation with selected diasporas, channels for diasporas&apos; support and investment towards safer shelters in the countries of origin, in ways that would be more targeted, effective and more compliant to international standards.</narrative>
  </description>
